						               													<description>Sporttable Box is a fusion between boardgames and Physical Activity.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On the board, you have the possibility of playing three different games: pursuit race, tug of war, and team sports. The gameplay is much alike that of party-games: the rules are easy to follow but, in order for you or your team to make strategic progress on the board, the players need to perform some active challenges (physical challenges with different levels of difficulty, by the way). These were carefully designed to create fun moments of challenge either against a goal, the timer or the opponent team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are more than 60 challenges divided into 4 categories: strength, dexterity, speed and mime (this one also provides a funny moment as it is about sports). So... roll the die, pick a card and let's get started! We are... SPORTACULAR!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
